<plot>This is a story about the extreme consequences of artistic delirium, aesthetic slavery, unexpressed talent and morbid imagination which degenerates into grave illness. It is a portrait of a mad man who is also damningly fascinating. It is the picture of two black and evil hearts that meet for fate's pleasure. It is a painting of an obscure and criminal side of the Piemontese province at the end of the 19th Century.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?309510</url></doc>
